CLI Host Manifest
===============================================================================

The CLI host manifest declares the provider and contexts exposed by the CLI host.

1. Provider
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```text
cli
```

2. Contexts
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```text
cli/env
cli/stdout
cli/stderr
```

3. Operations
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| Context | Operations |
|---------|------------|
| `env` | `read` |
| `stdout` | `write` |
| `stderr` | `write` |

4. Base URIs
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The materialized base URI shape is:

```text
cli://{instance}/env
cli://{instance}/stdout
cli://{instance}/stderr
```
